   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1897_AS_RBH_3_00016"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb190427" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">I. Wollzeile 15</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="1897_AS_RBH_3_00018"/><salute>Lieber Richard,</salute> Ich verga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s, da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s in
               jenem <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00726-1"/>Brief<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00726-1">nicht überliefert</note> von <rs ref="#pmb10765" type="person">Andrian</rs> auch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>teht, Sie mögen ihn <hi n="1" rend="underline">jedenfalls</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb33418" type="work"><hi rend="latintype">en route</hi></rs> von <rs ref="#pmb5449" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Huysmans</hi></rs> u. etwas über den <rs ref="#pmb42793" type="person">Milton</rs> (? unle<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>erlich)
               von <rs ref="#pmb28820" type="person"><hi rend="latintype">Stendhal</hi></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chicken.</p><p>Seine Adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <rs ref="#pmb228" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Baden Baden</hi></rs>, <pb facs="1897_AS_RBH_3_00019"/><rs ref="#pmb42783" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Sanatorium Frey</hi></rs>. –</p><p>Ich gehe vielleicht morgen (<date>So<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c>tag</date>)
                  <time>Abend</time> ins <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L00726-2"/><rs ref="#pmb118" type="place">Carltheater</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L00726-2"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> besuchte die Aufführung von <rs ref="#pmb42786" type="work">Der Stellvertreter</rs> von <rs ref="#pmb14723" type="person">William Busnach</rs> und <rs ref="#pmb6892" type="person">Georges
                     Duval</rs>.</note>.</p><closer>Herzlich Ihr<signed>Arthur.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
